metadata.name: Texture game
metadata.description:
This is a unique NFT.

It seems that these textures can not be combined.

The rope is designed for heavy work: tying boats, yachts, tying heavy logs, dragging wagons. To the touch, such a rope is very rough and unpleasant.

And the texture of the girl's skin is delicate, soft and fragile.

But look how they harmonize with each other! Me and my camera created a great balance between beauty and rawness.

The photo combines brutality and tenderness, smooth lines of the body and the rough texture of the wall, the softness of female skin and the roughness of the rope.

The rope is playfully intertwined on the model's body, emphasizing her beautiful figure.

Sunlight creates a beautiful pattern of light and shadow, highlighting the rough texture of the rope and the softness of the woman's skin. Droplets of water add romance and softness to the image. Light plays on the skin and rope, shimmers and creates a beautiful pattern.
